create or replace PROCEDURE         "BRF59A_MAPPING_PROCEDURE" (REPORT_DATE VARCHAR2) 
IS v_REPORT_DATE DATE := To_date (REPORT_DATE, 'DD-MM-YYYY'); 


BEGIN 

insert into BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE
(foracid, cust_id, ACCT_NAME,GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE,GL_CODE, SCHM_CODE,NRE_FLG,ACCT_CRNCY_CODE,REPORT_DATE,CONSTITUTION_CODE,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC,BACID,SOL_ID,NATIONALITY)
SELECT  ACCT_NUMBER,cust_id, ACCT_NAME,GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE, GL_CODE,SCHM_CODE,NRE_FLG,ACCT_CRNCY_CODE,REPORT_DATE,CONSTITUTION_CODE,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC,BACID,SOL_ID,NATIONALITY
FROM general_master_table WHERE report_date = '30-jun-2023';
COMMIT;

insert into BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE
(FORACID, ACCT_NAME,ACCT_CRNCY_CODE,REPORT_DATE,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC)
SELECT  ACCT_NO,ACCT_NAME,CURRENCY,REPORT_DATE,AMT_LC
FROM BRF_TREASURY_MASTER_TB WHERE report_date = '30-jun-2023';


--NDFI
UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59', report_addl_criteria_2 ='NBFI'
WHERE NVL(constitution_code,0) in ('11501', '11506', '11507','11599','NBFC','NBFC ',
'33107','33101','33103','33104','MXC','MXC  ','0')and GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE 
in ('13101','13201', '13206', '13215', '13216', '13217', '13220','13241', '24301', '24311','24312', '24313', '24319', '24503','24337','24626','13222') 
and SCHM_CODE IN ('CA108' ,'SB102','TD105','TD106') and 
sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008') and  ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC>=0 ;
COMMIT;
        
UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59', report_addl_criteria_2 ='NBFI'
WHERE constitution_code in ('11501', '11506', '11507','11599','NBFC','NBFC ',
'33107','33101','33103','33104','MXC','MXC  ')and GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE in ('13601','13611','13631','13641')  and  sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008')
and SCHM_CODE IN ('CA108' ,'SB102','TD105','TD106')
and  ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC>0 ;
COMMIT;

--INTERBANK_BORROWING -2
UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='INTERBANK_BORROWING'
WHERE FORACID IN ('A22010009','A22010004','A22010022','A22010029','A22010032','A22010040',
'A22010046','A22010054','A22010059','A22010060','A22010061','A22010078','A22010081')
AND ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC>0 ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='INTERBANK_BORROWING'
WHERE  FORACID IN ('L33130004','L33130003','L33130010','L33130011') ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='INTERBANK_BORROWING'
WHERE  FORACID IN ('L33130011') ;
COMMIT;

---GOV_PSE
UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='GOV_PSE'
WHERE CONSTITUTION_CODE  IN  ('SGOVT')AND GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE IN ('13101','13201', '13206', '13215', '13216', '13217', '13220','13241', '24301', '24311','24312', '24313', 
'24319', '24503', '24337')and  sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008') ;
COMMIT;


UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='GOV_PSE'
WHERE CONSTITUTION_CODE  IN  ('SGOVT')AND GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE IN ('13217', '13220', '13421') and 
sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008') ;
COMMIT;


UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='GOV_PSE'
WHERE CONSTITUTION_CODE  IN  ('SGOVT')AND GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE IN 
('13241', '13601', '13611', '13631', '13641') and  sol_id in 
('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008') ;
COMMIT;

--CORPORATE --63
UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='CORPORATE'
WHERE  NVL(constitution_code,0) in ('11409','11501','11502','11503','11504','11505','11506','11509','11599','11601','11602','11603',
		'11604','11605','11606','11607','11608','11699','22101','22201','22202','22301','22302','22303','22304','22305','22401','22402','22403','22404',
		'33101','33102', '33103','33104','33199','33201','33202','33203','33204','33299','45507','56500','56600','56601','56700','61001','61002','61003',
		'61004','61006','61007','61008','61010','61011','61012','61013','71001','71002','71004','71008','71009','71010','71011', '.', 'ASSOC','BFC','BFC ','BFC  ','BUEBC',
		'CLUBS','COOPB','COOPE','EDTRU','FGNBK','FGNCO','FGNSO','FGNSO ','FORNA','FZC','FZC ','FZC  ','FZCLL','FZE','FZE ','FZE  ','FZELL','GEMS','HUFJT','INSTU','JLC','JNTLG','JVC','LLTCO',
		'LSAA','MDBS','MXC','NFLLC','NGOGE','NGOOT','NGOSM','NGOSW','NPO','NPOSA','OFC','OFC ','OFC  ', 'OPLLC','PBCLI','PBCNL','PBPVT','PCLBG','PETRO','PJSC','PJSC ','PROPF',
		'PROPM','PROPR','PRTNF','PRTNR','PUBTR','PVJSC','PVTCO','PVTTR','REALE','REGSO','RFC','RFC ','RFC  ','RRB','SCC','SGOVT','SHGMA','SHGOT','SHGWE','SHGWO','SOCIE',
		'SPC','TRUST','ULTCO','DMCC','CC','SPLLC','SA','ESTB','REAL','','GOENT','GOVCO','GOVT','11700','0','FZLLC','BUC','11511','FZLLC ','BUC ')
        and  sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008')
		and GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE in ('13101','13201', '13206', '13215', '13216', '13217', '13220','13241', '24301', '24311','24312', '24313', '24319', '24503','24337','24626','13222')
     AND ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC>=0 AND NRE_FLG IN'Y';
COMMIT;


UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='CORPORATE'
WHERE BACID IN ('13201001','13246001','13291001') and  sol_id in
('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008') AND 
SCHM_CODE IN ('CA108' ,'SB102','TD105','TD106') ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='CORPORATE'
WHERE  NVL(constitution_code,0) in ('11501','11502','11503','11504','11505','11506','11509','11599','11601','11602','11603',
		'11604','11605','11606','11607','11608','11699','22101','22201','22202','22301','22302','22303','22304','22305','22401','22402','22403','22404',
		'33101','33102', '33103','33104','33199','33201','33202','33203','33204','33299','45507','56500','56600','56601','56700','61001','61002','61003',
		'61004','61006','61007','61008','61010','61011','61012','61013','71001','71002','71004','71008','71009','71010','71011', '.', 'ASSOC','BFC','BFC ','BFC  ','BUEBC',
		'CLUBS','COOPB','COOPE','EDTRU','FGNBK','FGNCO','FGNSO','FORNA','FZC','FZC ','FZC  ','FZCLL','FZE','FZE ','FZE  ','FZELL','GEMS','HUFJT','INSTU','JLC','JNTLG','JVC','LLTCO',
		'LSAA','MDBS','MXC','NFLLC','NGOGE','NGOOT','NGOSM','NGOSW','NPO','NPOSA','OFC','OFC ','OFC  ','OPLLC','PBCLI','PBCNL','PBPVT','PCLBG','PETRO','PJSC','PJSC ','PROPF',
		'PROPM','PROPR','PRTNF','PRTNR','PUBTR','PVJSC','PVTCO','PVTTR','REALE','REGSO','RFC','RFC ','RFC  ','RRB','SCC','SGOVT','SHGMA','SHGOT','SHGWE','SHGWO','SOCIE',
		'SPC','TRUST','ULTCO','DMCC','CC', 'SPLLC','SA','ESTB','REAL','GOENT','GOVCO','GOVT','11700','0')
		and GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE in ('13421') and  sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008')  AND ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC>=0
		and SCHM_CODE IN ('CA108' ,'SB102','TD105','TD106')  ;
        COMMIT;

UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='CORPORATE'
WHERE SCHM_CODE='TD103' AND GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE='13601'  AND constitution_code IS NULL ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='CORPORATE'
WHERE BACID IN ('15182006','15182001','13601004','13601003','13601002') and 
sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008') AND ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC>0
AND SCHM_CODE IN ('CA108' ,'SB102','TD105','TD106');
COMMIT;

--GRE
UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='GRE'
WHERE  constitution_code in ('CGPSU', 'SGPSU',  'QGOVT', '11401', '11403', '11404', 
'11405', '11406', '11407', '11408','11409') 
and GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE in ('13217', '13220', '13421') and 
sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008');
COMMIT;

UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='GRE'
WHERE  constitution_code in ('CGPSU', 'SGPSU',  'QGOVT', '11401', '11403', '11404', '11405', '11406', '11407', '11408','11409') 
and GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE in ('13241', '13601', '13611', '13631', '13641') and  
sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008');
COMMIT;

--Individuals 3,360,145

UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='INDIVIDUALS'
WHERE  NVL(constitution_code,0) in ('44101','44102','44103','44104','44105','44106','44107','44108','44109',
'44110','44111','44112','44113','44114','44115','44116','44199','44201','44202','44203','44204','44205','44206','44207','44208','44209',		'44210','44211','44212','44213','44214','44215','44216', '44217', '44299','71005','INDL','INDL ','INDVF','INDVM','NREIN','WPS','RESIN')
and GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE in ('13101','13201', '13206', '13215', '13216', '13217', '13220','13241', '24301', '24311','24312', '24313', '24319', '24503','24337','24626','13222')
and   NRE_FLG IN 'Y'
AND ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC>=0 and  sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008');
COMMIT;

       
UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='INDIVIDUALS'
WHERE  constitution_code in ('44101','44102','44103','44104','44105','44106','44107','44108','44109',
'44110','44111','44112','44113','44114','44115','44116','44199','44201','44202','44203','44204','44205','44206','44207','44208','44209',
'44210','44211','44212','44213','44214','44215','44216', '44217', '44299','71005','INDL','INDL ','INDVF','INDVM','NREIN','WPS','RESIN','NBFC','NBFC ')
and GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE in ('13421') AND NRE_FLG IN 'Y'  AND ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC>=0 and  sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008');
COMMIT;
 
UPDATE  BRF59A_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59' , report_addl_criteria_2 ='INDIVIDUALS'
WHERE  constitution_code in ('44101','44102','44103','44104','44105','44106','44107','44108','44109',
'44110','44111','44112','44113','44114','44115','44116','44199','44201','44202','44203','44204','44205','44206','44207','44208','44209',
'44210','44211','44212','44213','44214','44215','44216', '44217', '44299','71005','INDL','INDL ','INDVF','INDVM','NREIN','WPS','RESIN')
and GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE in ('13601','13611','13631','13641') AND NRE_FLG IN 'Y'
and  sol_id in ('9001','9002','9003','9004','9005','9008')
And  ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC>=0;
COMMIT;

-----
create or replace PROCEDURE         "BRF59B_MAPPING_PROCEDURE" (REPORT_DATE VARCHAR2) 
IS v_REPORT_DATE DATE := To_date (REPORT_DATE, 'DD-MM-YYYY'); 


BEGIN 

insert into BRF59B_MAPPING_TABLE
(foracid, cust_id, ACCT_NAME,GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE,GL_CODE, SCHM_CODE,NRE_FLG,ACCT_CRNCY_CODE,REPORT_DATE,CONSTITUTION_CODE,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC,BACID,SOL_ID,NATIONALITY)
SELECT  ACCT_NUMBER,cust_id, ACCT_NAME,GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE, GL_CODE,SCHM_CODE,NRE_FLG,ACCT_CRNCY_CODE,REPORT_DATE,CONSTITUTION_CODE,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC,BACID,SOL_ID,NATIONALITY
FROM general_master_table WHERE report_date = '30-jun-2023';
COMMIT;

insert into BRF59B_MAPPING_TABLE
(FORACID, ACCT_NAME,ACCT_CRNCY_CODE,REPORT_DATE,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC)
SELECT  ACCT_NO,ACCT_NAME,CURRENCY,REPORT_DATE,AMT_LC
FROM BRF_TREASURY_MASTER_TB WHERE report_date = '30-jun-2023';

--maturity date

--0 to 3 monthsROW102AP
update BRF59B_MAPPING_TABLE set REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59', report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW102AP' ,report_addl_criteria_3 = 'Canada' , REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102'
where  (NVL((MATURITY_DATE - REPORT_DATE), 0) <= 91) AND NATIONALITY ='CA';
commit;

--3 to 6 months ROW102AQ
update BRF59B_MAPPING_TABLE set REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59', report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW102AQ' ,report_addl_criteria_3 = 'Canada' , REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102'
where (NVL((MATURITY_DATE-REPORT_DATE),0)BETWEEN 92 AND 182)AND NATIONALITY ='CA';
commit;

--6 to 12 months ROW102AR
update BRF59B_MAPPING_TABLE set REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59', report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW102AR' ,report_addl_criteria_3 = 'Canada' , REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102'
where  (NVL((MATURITY_DATE-REPORT_DATE),0)BETWEEN 183 AND 363) AND NATIONALITY ='CA';
commit;
--over 1 year ROW102AS
update BRF59B_MAPPING_TABLE set REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59', report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW102AS' ,report_addl_criteria_3 = 'Canada' , REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102'
where (NVL((MATURITY_DATE-REPORT_DATE),0)>364) AND NATIONALITY ='CA';
commit;



--0 to 3 monthsROW103AP
update BRF59B_MAPPING_TABLE set REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59', report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW103AP' ,report_addl_criteria_3 = 'United States of America' , REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW103'
where  (NVL((MATURITY_DATE - REPORT_DATE), 0) <= 91) AND NATIONALITY ='US';
commit;

--3 to 6 months ROW103AQ
update BRF59B_MAPPING_TABLE set REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF59', report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW103AQ' ,report_addl_criteria_3 = 'United States of America' , REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW103'

------

create or replace PROCEDURE         "BRF59A_DETAIL_PROCEDURE" (REPORT_DATE VARCHAR2)
 
IS
 
  V_REPORT_DATE DATE := To_date (REPORT_DATE, 'DD-MM-YYYY');

BEGIN

delete from BRF59A_DETAILTABLE where report_date = v_report_date;

commit;

insert into BRF59A_DETAILTABLE
( foracid, cust_id, ACCT_NAME,REPORT_DATE,REPORT_LABEL_1,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,REPORT_NAME_1,COUNTRY,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC)
SELECT  foracid,cust_id, ACCT_NAME,REPORT_DATE,REPORT_LABEL_1,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,REPORT_NAME_1,NATIONALITY,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC
FROM brf59A_mapping_table  where report_date = V_REPORT_DATE AND REPORT_LABEL_1 IS NOT NULL;

insert into BRF59A_DETAILTABLE
( foracid, cust_id, ACCT_NAME,REPORT_DATE,REPORT_LABEL_1,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,REPORT_NAME_1,COUNTRY,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC)
SELECT  foracid,cust_id, ACCT_NAME,REPORT_DATE,REPORT_LABEL_1,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,REPORT_NAME_1,NATIONALITY,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC
FROM brf59B_mapping_table  where report_date = V_REPORT_DATE AND REPORT_LABEL_1 IS NOT NULL;


COMMIT;
END;
----

create or replace PROCEDURE         "BRF59B_DETAIL_PROCEDURE" (REPORT_DATE VARCHAR2)
 
IS
 
  V_REPORT_DATE DATE := To_date (REPORT_DATE, 'DD-MM-YYYY');

BEGIN

delete from BRF59B_DETAILTABLE where report_date = v_report_date;

commit;

MERGE INTO BRF59B_DETAILTABLE b
USING (
    SELECT 
      DISTINCT  COUNTRY,

        MAX(REPORT_LABEL_1) AS REPORT_LABEL_1,
        MAX(REPORT_NAME_1) AS REPORT_NAME_1,
        MAX(REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1) AS REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
        MAX(REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2) AS REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,
        MAX(REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3) AS REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,
        SUM(TotalBalance) AS TotalBalance
    FROM (
        SELECT 

            COUNTRY,
            REPORT_LABEL_1,
            REPORT_NAME_1,
            REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
            REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,
            REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,

            (SELECT SUM(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC) FROM BRF59A_DETAILTABLE WHERE COUNTRY = a.COUNTRY) AS TotalBalance
        FROM 
            BRF59A_DETAILTABLE a
    ) aggregated_data
    GROUP BY COUNTRY
) a ON (b.COUNTRY = a.COUNTRY AND b.REPORT_DATE = '30-jun-2023')
WHEN MATCHED THEN
    UPDATE SET 

        b.ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC = a.TotalBalance,
        b.REPORT_LABEL_1 = a.REPORT_LABEL_1,
        b.REPORT_NAME_1 = a.REPORT_NAME_1,
        b.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1 = a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
        b.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2 = a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,
        b.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3 = a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3

WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
    INSERT ( ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC, REPORT_DATE, REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,
    REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,REPORT_LABEL_1,REPORT_NAME_1)
    VALUES (a.TotalBalance, '30-JUN-2023',a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,
    a.REPORT_LABEL_1,a.REPORT_NAME_1);
COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF59B_DETAILTABLE
SET report_addl_criteria_4 = ('REMAINING_COUNTRIES'),R1_NBFI2 = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF59A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW182AJ' 
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW182' ;
COMMIT;
UPDATE BRF59B_DETAILTABLE
SET report_addl_criteria_4 = ('REMAINING_COUNTRIES'),R1_INTERBANK2 = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF59A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW182AK' 
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW182' ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF59B_DETAILTABLE
SET report_addl_criteria_4 = ('REMAINING_COUNTRIES'),R1_GOV5 = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF59A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW182AL' 
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW182' ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF59B_DETAILTABLE
SET report_addl_criteria_4 = ('REMAINING_COUNTRIES'),R1_CORPORATE2 = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF59A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW182AM' 
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW182' ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF59B_DETAILTABLE
SET report_addl_criteria_4 = ('REMAINING_COUNTRIES'),R1_GRE2 = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF59A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW182AN' 
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW182' ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF59B_DETAILTABLE
SET report_addl_criteria_4 = ('REMAINING_COUNTRIES'),R1_INDIVIDUALS3 = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF59A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW182AO' 
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW182' ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF59B_DETAILTABLE
SET report_addl_criteria_4 = ('REMAINING_COUNTRIES'),R1_ZERO1 = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF59A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_1 = 'ROW182AP' 
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW182' ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF59B_DETAILTABLE
SET report_addl_criteria_4 = ('REMAINING_COUNTRIES'),R1_THREE1 = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))

COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF59B_DETAILTABLE
SET report_addl_criteria_4 = ('REMAINING_COUNTRIES'),R1_SIX1 = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))

insert into BRF59E_SUMMARYTABLE(
NBFI2,INTERBANK2,GOV5,CORPORATE2,GRE2,INDIVIDUALS3,ZERO1,THREE1,SIX1,ONEYEAR1,REPORT_DATE,
ROW_LABEL,COUNTRY_BREAK_DOWN,remaining)
select R1_NBFI2,R1_INTERBANK2,R1_GOV5,R1_CORPORATE2,R1_GRE2,R1_INDIVIDUALS3,R1_ZERO1,R1_THREE1,
R1_SIX1,R1_ONEYEAR1,REPORT_DATE,REPORT_LABEL_1,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_4,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3 from 
BRF59B_DETAILTABLE where REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE and
report_addl_criteria_4 = ('REMAINING_COUNTRIES');

((V_R73_BANKS2+V_R73_GOV3+V_R73_OTHERS2+V_R73_BANKS3+V_R73_GOV4+V_R73_OTHERS3)+V_R73_FOREIGN1) THEN

 UPDATE BRF59E_SUMMARYTABLE
SET EMPTY = 
    CASE 
        WHEN (
            ( V_NBFI+ V_INTERBANK+ V_GOV+ V_CORPORATE+ V_GRE+ V_TRADE+
             V_INDIVIDUALS+ V_INVESTMENT+ V_NBFI1+ V_INTERBANK1+ V_GOV1+
             V_CORPORATE1+ V_GRE1+ V_TRADE1+ V_INDIVIDUALS1+ V_INVESTMENT1)+
             V_FOREIGN-( V_BANKS+ V_GOV2+ V_OTHER)+
            ( V_BANKS1+ V_INDIVIDUALS2+ V_OTHER1)
        ) = (
            ( V_BANKS2+ V_GOV3+ V_OTHERS2+ V_BANKS3+ V_GOV4+ V_OTHERS3)+
             V_FOREIGN1
        ) THEN 'TRUE'
        ELSE 'FALSE'
    END
WHERE REPORT_DATE =  '30-jun-2023';


SELECT SUM(INVESTMENT) INTO total_investment FROM BRF59E_SUMMARYTABLE;

    -- Update all rows with the computed total investment
    UPDATE BRF59E_SUMMARYTABLE
    SET REM_INVESTMENT = total_investment;
    
    -- Commit the transaction
    COMMIT;
    
    update BRF59E_SUMMARYTABLE set REM_INTERBANK =(SELECT SUM(INTERBANK) 
FROM BRF59E_SUMMARYTABLE);
